* TEST 03: Compare and Match
* Tests COMPARE, IF EQUAL, IF LESS, IF GREATER

(0)  INPUT MASTER FILE-A TRANS FILE-B ; OUTPUT MATCHED FILE-C .

(1)  READ-ITEM A ; IF END OF DATA GO TO OPERATION 6 ;
     READ-ITEM B ; IF END OF DATA GO TO OPERATION 6 .

(2)  COMPARE KEY (A) WITH KEY (B) ;
     IF EQUAL GO TO OPERATION 3 ;
     IF LESS GO TO OPERATION 4 ;
     OTHERWISE GO TO OPERATION 5 .

(3)  TRANSFER A TO C ;
     MOVE VALUE (B) TO MATCHED-VALUE (C) ;
     WRITE-ITEM C ;
     JUMP TO OPERATION 1 .

(4)  READ-ITEM A ; IF END OF DATA GO TO OPERATION 6 ;
     JUMP TO OPERATION 2 .

(5)  READ-ITEM B ; IF END OF DATA GO TO OPERATION 6 ;
     JUMP TO OPERATION 2 .

(6)  STOP .

